scene.message:
Mark: H-hey...{nl}
It vanished!!{waitkey}What do we do?!{nl}
We can't get back like this!!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: .........{wait_fr:88}{nl}
Something must've happened{nl}
in Sonomura's heart...{waitkey}{clearbox}With Kandori gone,{nl}
only she could do{nl}
something like this.{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: ...{wait_fr:88}What about{nl}
Kandori's mirror?{nl}
Order it to send us back.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Mark!{nl}
If we ask Kandori's mirror,{nl}
can't we reach that town?!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: That's it!!{nl}
We've still got Kandori's{nl}
mirror!! Just ask it!{waitkey}Send us to that town, we say!!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Hey, Kandori's mirror!{nl}
Just ask it, right?{nl}
Take us to that town, say!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: ...{wait_fr:60}Is Sonomura{nl}
refusing us?!{nl}
I can't think otherwise.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Damn it!!{nl}
What do we do... what...{wait_fr:104}{nl}
Hm?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: This is...{nl}
did Sonomura drop it...{wait_fr:88}{nl}
What good is just{nl}
this left behind...{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: Hey, this Sonomura{nl}
has a compact{nl}
on her too.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Hey!{nl}
The original Maki has{nl}
a Compact too!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Hey!{nl}
The real Maki's got{nl}
a compact too?!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Ah!!{nl}
The real Sonomura's got{nl}
a compact too!!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Let me see...{wait_fr:88}{nl}
The real Sonomura's compact{nl}
and the ideal one...{waitkey}The real one has the{nl}
mirror set in it, but...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Please!!{nl}
Send us back into{nl}
Sonomura's heart!{waitkey}{nl}
...{wait_fr:30}{wait_fr:30}{wait_fr:30}{wait_fr:30}{wait_fr:30}{wait_fr:30}{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}{wait_fr:30}{wait_fr:30}{wait_fr:30}{wait_fr:30}{wait_fr:30}{wait_fr:30}...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: The real compact{nl}
couldn't have such power...{nl}
If only...{waitkey}If the ideal Sonomura's{nl}
compact were complete,{nl}
there'd have been a chance...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Maki...{nl}
Everyone's waiting, y'know?{nl}
You don't have to{nl}
suffer alone.{waitkey}{clearbox}Please, call out to us...{nl}
I'll go however far it{nl}
takes...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: The ideal Sonomura{nl}
is the form of her wish{nl}
to change herself.{waitkey}But that ideal heart itself{nl}
has come to deny{nl}
her own existence...{waitkey}{clearbox}Sonomura...{nl}
have you truly lost hope?{waitkey}{clearbox}If even a shard remains,{nl}
then call out to us...{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: Sonomura!!{nl}
Don't run away!{nl}
Running is the easy part...{waitkey}{clearbox}My mother was the woman{nl}
of Kandori's old man...{nl}
Tossed out like a dirty rag.{waitkey}{clearbox}She bore me knowing{nl}
she'd be cast aside...{nl}
You know why?{waitkey}{clearbox}She said a parent{nl}
can't throw away{nl}
their own child's life...{waitkey}{clearbox}You've got a mother too...{nl}
No parent fails to love{nl}
their child.{waitkey}Go home, to your mother.{nl}
Now wake up, dammit!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Maki!{nl}
Please wake up! Please...{waitkey}{clearbox}Maki's not the only one{nl}
who suffers with many{nl}
selves inside...{waitkey}{clearbox}Everyone says I'm refined,{nl}
that I'm pretty,{nl}
but it's not really true...{waitkey}{clearbox}I was always putting on{nl}
a front. When a boy talks{nl}
of another girl,{nl}
I just can't bear it.{waitkey}{clearbox}So I always force a smile...{nl}
It was so stifling...{nl}
An awful girl, aren't I?{waitkey}{clearbox}But I've realized what{nl}
matters are friends you can{nl}
open your heart to-{nl}
everyone here.{waitkey}{clearbox}There's someone I like now.{nl}
Probably the same person{nl}
as you, Maki...{nl}
Please, wake up...{waitkey}{clearbox}Let's talk about him and{nl}
all sorts of things, okay?{nl}
Please...{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Maki, wake up!{nl}
I'll tell you a funny{nl}
story I've been saving!{waitkey}{clearbox}Me... they call me 'Brown,'{nl}
right? It's a nickname{nl}
from junior high...{waitkey}{clearbox}Everyone thinks it's 'cause{nl}
of my brown hair...{nl}
but really, {wait_fr:96}it's 'cause{nl}
I pooped my pants.{waitkey}{clearbox}See? Funny, right? It's true.{nl}
Pathetic, huh? In junior high?{nl}
The whole school's joke...{waitkey}{clearbox}It was so humiliating...{nl}
I came to Hermelin because{nl}
I couldn't stay in{nl}
my hometown.{waitkey}{clearbox}So in high school I made{nl}
up a new self, struck poses,{nl}
acted all cool, fooling{nl}
myself the whole time...{waitkey}{clearbox}But I'm done with that.{nl}
Watching you, Maki, made me{nl}
see how dumb I was being...{waitkey}{clearbox}See? Laugh for me, won't you?{nl}
I'm begging you...{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Wake up, Sonomura!{nl}
You still haven't returned{nl}
my handkerchief, y'know.{nl}
Ayase'll hear you out...{waitkey}{clearbox}Ayase gets how you feel,{nl}
Sonomura. Ayase's thought{nl}
the same things too...{nl}
'Let the future vanish'...{waitkey}{clearbox}I think I acted dumb all{nl}
the time 'cause I'm scared{nl}
of the future... Thinking{nl}
about it gets you down, right?{waitkey}{clearbox}So I think I ran away,{nl}
telling myself as long as{nl}
now is good... But that's{nl}
not right, is it...{waitkey}{clearbox}It's my own future.{nl}
I've gotta decide it myself...{nl}
Ayase's decided.{waitkey}{clearbox}Catch a nice guy and{nl}
live easy! Sonomura...{nl}
tell me your dream too...{nl}
I'm begging you...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: What is it, {ctl0f:1}?{wait_fr:88}{nl}
A shard of Kandori's mirror?!{waitkey}{clearbox}This size, this shape...{nl}
it looks like it'd fit{nl}
Sonomura's compact!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: For real?!{nl}
That might get us back!{nl}
Hand it over, {ctl0f:1}!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Where are you going?{nl}
Do you mean to leave{nl}
Sonomura like this?{waitkey}{ret}

The Mirror of Chaos is{nl}
shattered... What could have{nl}
happened in the town of{nl}
Maki's heart...{waitkey}{ret}

It's the 'Door to Paradise'{nl}
Maki painted... What feelings{nl}
did she paint this{nl}
picture with...{waitkey}{ret}

It's a hologram of the{nl}
Deva System. It seems Maki{nl}
is linked directly to{nl}
the system.{waitkey}{ret}
